text: Lee Hye-jin (born 16 November 1985) is a South Korean sport shooter who competed in the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female sport shooters Category:ISSF rifle shooters Category:Olympic shooters of South Korea Category:Shooters at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 2006 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in shooting Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 2006 Asian Games
